title: Cuttlefish rice
description: It's too salty. My experiences in Nice ruined my good impression for French cuisine.

title: Ponte Sant'Angelo
description: This is the saint angel bridge. It was designed by Bernini.

title: White houses, like a poster
description: Every photo I took here looks like a poster. It's extremely beautiful. A city of white and blue.

title: Me in front of the Parthenon
description: Standing there, it feels sacred.

title: La Sagrada Familia
description: Saint Family Church. Gaudi's unfinished master piece. The light inside are all natural! It's amazing!

title: Suprise: Athens is full of graffiti
description: Athens in my mind is the where one of the earliest civilizations started. So when I see the graffities on the walls, trains, grounds... I'm really shocked!

title: Houses
description: The streets and houses make me feel I'm in a quiet small city. There's a umbrella on each window. I guess it's because here it often suddenly rains.

title: Super Nice Land Lady
description: Our land lady is a beatiful young girl. She's very polite and kind. She also gave us a bottle of wine as a gift! This is the first gift I've ever received from an Airbnb land lord.

title: Vanilla Scented Candles
description: Our house is beatiful and full of the scent of vanilla aromatherapy. We also watched a movie in the living room at the last day there.

title: Atticus Odeon
description: This is one of the two ancient theatres on the acropolis. The other is Theatre of Dionysos. It is astonishing to see one of the earliest theatres!

title: The Blue Church
description: Probably the most famouse scene on Santorini.

title: I love Italian food!
description: This is our first meal in Rome. It's wonderful! We've been eating greek food for 3 days and I was already sick of it. Italian food saved me. This is a steak.

title: First Pasta in Rome
description: The mushroom really goes well with the pasta. But it's a little too salty for us.

title: TIRAMISU!!!
description: POMPI, this is the place our landlord recommended~ It's delicious, and cheap.

title: With a rose?
description: There're lots of (Indian?) vendors in Rome. They're so tricky. They kind of forced us to buy this rose. Though I love it~ and the hat lol. This is near the fountain.

title: Stairs to top of Vatican
description: This is the stairs goes to the top of the church in Vatican. The whole way is so narrow, even for a small asian girl like me. And it's spiral like this.

title: Pop Art Museum in Nice
description: Finally the Renaissance is the past. Welcome to modern art.

title: By the beach
description: It's extremely relaxing sitting by the golden sealine.

title: Sangria
description: The left one is the famouse local wine -- Sangria. It's sweet and delicious~

title: Fragonard
description: This photo is from google

title: Fun time in Tibidabo
description: We had great time here, though it's a small amusement park
